A Nigerian lady identified as Eunie Daisy has told of how she escaped dying in the hands a of a stray bullet. According to Eunie who shared the story of what happened on her Facebook page, she was in her room when the stray bullet broke in through the ceiling and landed on the floor. Luckily no one was hit by it. The lady explained that the sound of gunshot was not heard when the bullet broke into the room so it must have come from far away from where she lived. Eunie thanked God for sparing her life and shared a video from her house showing the bullet. Source